

## **3. Descriptive Statistics**  
### **Key Concepts:**  
- **Mean** (Arithmetic, Weighted)  
- **Median** (Robustness, Odd/Even Data)  
- **Mode** (Unimodal/Bimodal)  
- **Standard Deviation** (σ vs. s)  
- Skewness & Kurtosis  

### **Study Resources:**  
- **Video Lectures:**  
  - [CrashCourse - Statistics (YouTube)](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zouPoc49xkg)  
  - [NPTEL - Descriptive Stats (IIT Madras)](https://nptel.ac.in/courses/111/106/111106090/)  
- **Textbooks:**  
  - *Statistics for Engineers* – Montgomery & Runger (Ch. 1-2)  
  - *Higher Engineering Mathematics* – B.S. Grewal  
- **Practice Problems:**  
